HEADWORD: Hood moulding
<hw>Hood" mould`ing</hw> }</mhw>
<pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Arch.)</fld> <def>A projecting molding over the head
of an arch, forming the outermost member of the archivolt; -- called
also <altname>hood mold</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

